Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:47.94,AKT,Yume,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san? Hej, Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:49.53,Alt Text,Yoshiyuki,0020,0020,0000,,Uh, ako to vysvetliť? Netvárte sa tak nahnevane.
